tinuation of any coadministered medication that is known to affect the liver.', 'Synergism', 'Dexfenfluramine, Ephedrine, Phentermine, Lorcaserin, Diethylpropion, Mazindol', 'Brivaracetam, Ezogabine, Cenobamate, Methylphenobarbital, Ethosuximide, Lacosamide, Tiagabine, Ethotoin, Rufinamide, Paramethadione, Perampanel, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/55089/', '[1] "Product Information. Epidiolex (cannabidiol)." Greenwich Biosciences Inc, Carlsbad, CA.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Epidiolex (cannabidiol)." Greenwich Biosciences Inc, Carlsbad, CA.', 1767369485);
